'''Autofiring [[Laser cannon/Legends|laser cannons]]''' were set up as booby traps by poachers and other factions to destroy ships of those trying to scan or search abandoned starships in space, particular [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] in nature. They would activate when crews tripped an alarm. The ''[[Foresight]]'' was one ship destroyed by an autofiring laser cannon.

